longBusinessSummary: Indef Manufacturing Limited provides material handling solutions. Its products include cranes, wire ropes and manual hoists, electric chain hoists, ergonomic handling solutions, and storage and retrieval products. The company serves oil and gas, engineering, auto and auto ancillary, cement, metals, and other industries. Indef Manufacturing Limited was incorporated in 2022 and is based in Navi Mumbai, India.
